item.title: Help immediately
item.dc:creator: @No_Life2 No Life
item.description:
@No_Life2 wrote:

This isn’t really detailed enough for us to help you with your specific problem (even if it printed the stack trace).

From my experience, this problem occurs because your Update.java or CacheDownloader.java files don’t have the correct configurations, (e.g. links, cache name, cache version, zip file name, etc).

I’m assuming this is a [PI] so I’m just going to recommend replacing your Update and CacheDownloader java files with the ones from the Hybrid PVP v3 source, found here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=487174.0
